   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4544e064",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "To ensure the dataset is representative, we analyze text length and diversity. The CNN/DailyMail dataset includes a wide range of topics (e.g., politics, business, international news), making it suitable for general-purpose summarization tasks.\n",
    "\n",
    "Balancing in this context refers to:\n",
    "\n",
    "Variation in text lengths\n",
    "Diversity of topics\n",
    "Consistent structure (article-summary pairs)"
   ]
  },
